{"id":293368,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-加拿大籍归国华侨何剑明被骗投资三亚当/","date":"2013-05-13T14:46:05Z","modified":"2013-05-13T14:46:05Z","title":"维权网 | 加拿大籍归国华侨何剑明被骗投资,三亚当局包庇犯罪分子（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李悠然报道）</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日凌晨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">55</span><span>分</span><span>，一伙不明身份的人，开着铲车将三亚市政府动用了上百警力才帮助何剑明先生修建好用于保护他生命财产安全的围墙给推毁。何剑明报警后，距离事发地点仅</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>公里</span><span>的派出所，一个多小时以后才到达现场。</span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span>事后，犯罪嫌疑人王堂珍承认是其指使人干的，但至今公安机关还没有对犯罪分子采取强制措施。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">     </span></div>\n<div><span>何剑明先生是加拿大籍归国华侨，据他介绍</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span>他是被三亚某派出所所长使用伪造国家印章公文等手段</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>骗到三亚进行投资</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,2007</span><span>年报案后，经公安机关侦查证据确凿</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>但检察院却以“犯罪嫌疑人主观上是否具有非法占有的目的，事实不清证据不足”为由不予起诉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>何剑明向海南省检察院申诉还是维持了原决定。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span>而检察院用于认定“犯罪嫌疑人主观上是否具有非法占有的目的，事实不清证据不足”的一份署名为王堂珍且未经过鉴定的“承诺书”上承诺于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>年底就应当退还给何剑明先生的投资款，时至今日却还没有兑现。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span>而在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年，王堂良指使其家人王堂珍等人多次长时间对何剑明先生实施犯罪行为，何剑明打过无数次</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>报警电话，警察却从来没有受理，连笔录也没有做过，并且参与“协调”他们的纠纷，迫使何剑明将已经出租给别人的年租金</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">60</span><span>万的酒店，用置换的方式租给王堂良的母亲，根据法律</span><span></span><span>规定已经构成“强迫交易”罪，但公安机关却拒绝履行其职责。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">   </span></div>\n<div><span>不得已，何先生只好在自己的屋檐上打起了横幅，横幅上写着“三亚市城郊检察院执法不公造成黑社会猖獗”。引来过路游客经常驻足观望。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>何剑明电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13876454677</span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-kgAf-zlJzko/UZD10_jM6zI/AAAAAAAAh6s/cLKQ2Oa2DDM/s1600/P1050819.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-kgAf-zlJzko/UZD10_jM6zI/AAAAAAAAh6s/cLKQ2Oa2DDM/s400/P1050819.JPG\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-gWXBMB12Mzs/UZD1v7z9lfI/AAAAAAAAh6Y/OtfXeksaugA/s1600/nEO_IMG_P1050812.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-gWXBMB12Mzs/UZD1v7z9lfI/AAAAAAAAh6Y/OtfXeksaugA/s400/nEO_IMG_P1050812.jpg\" width=\"300\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-s8983R_oVsU/UZD1zqEYjnI/AAAAAAAAh6g/2iwU0a-gHsU/s1600/nEO_IMG_P1050813.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-s8983R_oVsU/UZD1zqEYjnI/AAAAAAAAh6g/2iwU0a-gHsU/s400/nEO_IMG_P1050813.jpg\" width=\"300\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-9MB6GREqpBA/UZD10hZBuwI/AAAAAAAAh6o/FmmcwcverYw/s1600/nEO_IMG_P1050814.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-9MB6GREqpBA/UZD10hZBuwI/AAAAAAAAh6o/FmmcwcverYw/s400/nEO_IMG_P1050814.jpg\" width=\"300\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-EqmiehtP1K0/UZD13Pu4hII/AAAAAAAAh64/IZn9NdDND8w/s1600/nEO_IMG_P1050815.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-EqmiehtP1K0/UZD13Pu4hII/AAAAAAAAh64/IZn9NdDND8w/s400/nEO_IMG_P1050815.jpg\" width=\"300\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Ra9YrE6Xv2w/UZD18dwtHvI/AAAAAAAAh7M/cVe8fif1y8A/s1600/nEO_IMG_P1050816.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Ra9YrE6Xv2w/UZD18dwtHvI/AAAAAAAAh7M/cVe8fif1y8A/s400/nEO_IMG_P1050816.jpg\" width=\"300\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-mzi6KlD9ZIk/UZD17Ab-8HI/AAAAAAAAh7A/irPJLQdGKOU/s1600/nEO_IMG_P1050817.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-mzi6KlD9ZIk/UZD17Ab-8HI/AAAAAAAAh7A/irPJLQdGKOU/s400/nEO_IMG_P1050817.jpg\" width=\"300\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Hb6BTjhC5V8/UZD18DkzlmI/AAAAAAAAh7I/QgvrcqyhU1c/s1600/nEO_IMG_P1050818.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Hb6BTjhC5V8/UZD18DkzlmI/AAAAAAAAh7I/QgvrcqyhU1c/s400/nEO_IMG_P1050818.jpg\" width=\"300\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,14492]}